han.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/star-wars-jedi-survivor-third-game-confirmed-cameron-monaghan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/star-wars-jedi-survivor-third-game-confirmed-cameron-monaghan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/star-wars-jedi-survivor-third-game-confirmed-cameron-monaghan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/star-wars-jedi-survivor-third-game-confirmed-cameron-monaghan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/star-wars-jedi-survivor-third-game-confirmed-cameron-monaghan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/star-wars-jedi-fallen-order"><em>《星球大战绝地：陨落的</em></a>武士团》及其续集<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/star-wars-jedi-survivor"><em>《幸存者》</em></a>中扮演卡尔·凯斯蒂斯的卡梅隆·莫纳汉确认了该系列第三款游戏的存在。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/features/gaming-features/the-best-games-of-2023-so-far-zelda-diablo-final-fantasy-3468532">2023 年最佳游戏……到目前为止！</a></strong></li></ul><p>在今年佛罗里达州奥卡拉动漫展的一个小组中，莫纳汉表示，第三部<em>《星球大战绝地武士》</em>游戏正在发生变化。然而，根据他的说法，生产似乎尚未开始。</p><p> “我们现在正在这样做。所以这是一项艰巨的任务，到目前为止已经进行了一些对话，但希望当所有的事情都说完并完成后，我们将能够再次为你们制作一些非常酷的东西，”他解释道（通过<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N9t3Vd1VWC0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube</a> ）。</p><p>这两款游戏的导演斯蒂格·阿斯穆森（Stig Asmussen）此前曾确认，该系列的想法是制作成三部曲。 </p><figure id="attachment_3425135" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3425135" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3425135" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Star-Wars-Jedi-Survivor-credit-electronic-arts.jpg" alt="星球大战绝地：幸存者。信用：EA。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Star-Wars-Jedi-Survivor-credit-electronic-arts.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Star-Wars-Jedi-Survivor-credit-electronic-arts-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Star-Wars-Jedi-Survivor-credit-electronic-arts-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Star-Wars-Jedi-Survivor-credit-electronic-arts-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Star-Wars-Jedi-Survivor-credit-electronic-arts-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Star-Wars-Jedi-Survivor-credit-electronic-arts-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3425135" class="wp-caption-text"> 《星球大战绝地：幸存者》图片来源：Electronic Arts</figcaption></figure><p> “除了我们在第一款游戏中所做的事情之外，我们如何才能将卡尔和团队带到新的地方？”他在三月份<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/star-wars-jedi-survivor-director-wants-to-make-cals-saga-a-trilogy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">接受<em>IGN</em>采访</a>时做出了回应。</p><p> “我们对《幸存者》的举办时间框架、赌注是什么、游戏基调是什么有一个相当不错的想法……而且我们还知道除此之外我们还可以做些什么。”</p><p>阿斯穆森还表示，“相当安全的假设”是，第三款游戏将使用虚幻引擎 5 而不是其前身构建。话虽如此， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/respawn-entertainment-3">Respawn Entertainment</a>在<em>《幸存者》</em>中将这一引擎推向了更高的高度。</p><p> “ <em>《绝地：幸存者》的</em>优势在于提供了令人惊叹的<em>星球大战</em>世界、精彩的战斗和 AAA 级动作冒险，内容精致、有趣且内容丰富，” <em>NME</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/star-wars-jedi-survivor-review-3435716#:~:text=It's%20not%20just%20the%20white,full%20of%20stuff%20to%20do.">续集的五星级评论</a>中说道，并补充道它“[感觉]真正是下一代”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3477588" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3477588" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3477588" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/star-wars-jedi-survivor-coming-to-xbox-one-and-ps4.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/star-wars-jedi-survivor-coming-to-xbox-one-and-ps4.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/star-wars-jedi-survivor-coming-to-xbox-one-and-ps4-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-conte